# Design System Guide

## Theme & Colors

**Base**: Dark theme with pure black background (`bg-black`)

**Text Hierarchy**:
- Primary: `text-white`
- Secondary: `text-gray-300`
- Muted: `text-gray-400`

**Accent Colors** (use for gradients, highlights, interactive states):
- Cyan: `#22D3EE` / `cyan-400`
- Purple: `#8B5CF6` / `purple-500`
- Pink: `#EC4899` / `pink-400`
- Blue: `#60A5FA` / `blue-400`

**Gradient Patterns**:
```tsx
// Section title gradient
"bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 via-purple-500 to-pink-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent"

// Card accent gradient
"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 via-purple-500 to-pink-500"

// Background orbs
"bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500/20 to-purple-500/20 blur-3xl"
```

## Typography

**Font**: Geist Sans (loaded via `next/font/google`)

**Headings**:
- Hero: `text-7xl lg:text-9xl font-bold tracking-tight`
- Section: `text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-bold` or `font-black`
- Card Title: `text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold`

**Body**: `text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300/400 leading-relaxed`

**Labels**: `text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider`

## Animation Patterns (Framer Motion)

**Page Entry**:
```tsx
initial={{ opacity: 0 }}
animate={{ opacity: 1 }}
transition={{ duration: 0.8 }}
```

**Scroll-triggered (use `react-intersection-observer`)**:
```tsx
const [ref, inView] = useInView({ threshold: 0.1, triggerOnce: true });

// Staggered container
const containerVariants = {
  hidden: { opacity: 0 },
  visible: {
    opacity: 1,
    transition: { staggerChildren: 0.2, delayChildren: 0.2 }
  }
};

// Child items
const itemVariants = {
  hidden: { y: 60, opacity: 0 },
  visible: { y: 0, opacity: 1 }
};
```

**Spring Config**:
```tsx
transition={{ type: "spring", stiffness: 200, damping: 25 }}
```

**Hover Interactions**:
```tsx
whileHover={{ scale: 1.02, y: -2 }}
whileTap={{ scale: 0.98 }}
```

**Infinite Animations** (backgrounds, decorative elements):
```tsx
animate={{ scale: [1, 1.2, 1], opacity: [0.3, 0.6, 0.3] }}
transition={{ duration: 3, repeat: Infinity, ease: "easeInOut" }}
```

## Glass Morphism

**Standard Glass Card**:
```tsx
"bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl"
```

**Navigation Glass**:
```tsx
// In globals.css
.glass-nav {
  background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  box-shadow: 
    inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05),
    inset 0 1px 0 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}
```

**Hover Glow Effect**:
```tsx
"group-hover:border-white/20 group-hover:bg-white/10"
// Or with color
"group-hover:border-cyan-400/30"
```

## Component Patterns

**Section Layout**:
```tsx
<section className="min-h-screen py-24 px-6 relative overflow-hidden bg-black">
  <div className="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    {/* Background decorative elements with blur */}
    {/* Section header */}
    {/* Content grid */}
  </div>
</section>
```

**LiquidCard (3D tilt on hover)**:
- Uses `useMotionValue`, `useSpring`, `useTransform` for mouse-tracking tilt
- Subtle border animation: `animate={{ opacity: [0.3, 0.6, 0.3] }}`
- Wrapper with `perspective-1000` and `transform-gpu`

**ElasticButton**:
```tsx
<motion.button
  whileHover={{ scale: 1.02 }}
  whileTap={{ scale: 0.98 }}
  className="px-8 py-4 bg-white text-black font-semibold rounded-full"
>
```

**Tech/Tag Pills**:
```tsx
"px-4 py-2 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg text-sm text-gray-300"
// Hover: "hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white/20"
```

**Timeline**:
- Vertical line: `w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-blue-500/50 to-transparent`
- Node: `w-6 h-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-500 rounded-full`
- Alternating card placement: `index % 2 === 0 ? 'justify-start' : 'justify-end'`

## Background Decorations

**Gradient Orbs**:
```tsx
<div className="absolute top-1/4 -right-48 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl" />
```

**Dot Grid**:
```tsx
style={{
  backgroundImage: `radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 1px, transparent 0)`,
  backgroundSize: "48px 48px",
}}
```

**Floating Particles**:
```tsx
// Random positioned, animated with y movement and opacity pulse
animate={{ y: [0, -30, 0], opacity: [0.3, 0.8, 0.3] }}
```

## Performance

- Use `will-change-transform transform-gpu` on animated elements
- Lazy load images below the fold
- Use `useMemo` for static arrays/configs
- Lenis for smooth scrolling: `duration: 1.2, smoothWheel: true`

## Key Libraries

- `framer-motion` - all animations
- `react-intersection-observer` - scroll triggers
- `lenis` - smooth scrolling
- `react-icons` - iconography (FaGithub, FaLinkedin, etc.)
- `@heroicons/react` - UI icons
- `next/image` - optimized images
